amount of more than 0 DM results"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "Is there only forestry or an agricultural and forestry activity i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "of \u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "1c EStG, the values \u200b\u200bof which exceed DM 4000 in total, a determination of profits according to Section 13a Paragraphs 2 to 5 EStG is ruled out"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "Farmers and foresters whose profit would have to be determined in accordance with Section 13a Paragraphs 2 to 6 EStG can apply to determine their profit for four consecutive financial years on the basis of voluntary bookkeeping in accordance with Section 4 Paragraph 1 EStG or Section 4 Paragraph 3 EStG"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The application must be made in writing and irrevocably no later than six months after the end of the financial year to which it relates (Section 13a (1) EStG)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "If a farmer or forester does not meet the obligation, the profit must be estimated"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "2 The basic amount (\u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 EStG) assessment basis for the basic amount is the amount according to \u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "1 to 5 of the Income Tax Act"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The twelfth part of the starting value is to be used as the basic amount"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The in \u00a7 13a Abs 3 no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "1 of the Income Tax Act (EStG), the comparative values \u200b\u200band hectare values \u200b\u200bcan be found in the standard value notification"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The decisive factor for determining the initial value is the unit value that was determined on the last determination time, which is before the beginning of the financial year or coincides with the beginning of the financial year for which the profit is to be determined"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "For the determination of profits to be carried out for the first time in accordance with Section 13a of the Income Tax Act, the last main date of assessment is 1 1 1964. The last update or subsequent assessment date is 1 1 1974 because updates and subsequent assessments are made on this key date for the first time"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "However, if the circumstances that led to an update or subsequent determination have occurred before the start of the financial year in which the update or subsequent determination occurs, the updated or subsequently established unit value of the profit determination for this financial year is decisive"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "Example: A farmer bought four hectares of agricultural land on 1 3 1974"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "On the 1 1 1975 is gem"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "22 BewG carried out a value update"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The unit value updated to 1 1 1975 is already used for the determination of profits according to \u00a7 13a EStG of the fiscal year"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "1974/75 decisive"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The definitive standard assessment is a basic assessment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "If a unit value that is decisive for determining the profit is corrected or updated, the income tax assessments based thereon are to be changed ex officio (Section 218 (4) AO)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The income tax assessment cannot be challenged on the grounds that the underlying standard value assessment is incorrect"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "This objection can only be asserted in the appeal proceedings against the standard value notification (Section 232 (2) AO)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "3 De