ves employed in the business without an employment contract (\u00a7 10 StAnpG) is according to \u00a7 13a para 4 no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "5 of the Income Tax Act (EStG) for the number of full-time employees (VAK) appropriate to the type and size of the company"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "Paid workers are to be counted towards the appropriate number of VAK according to the length of their employment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "For areas of agricultural use (\u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "1 a EStG) a maximum of 007 VAK per hectare are to be applied"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "For the other values \u200b\u200bbelonging to the initial value (\u00a7 13a Paragraph 3 No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "1 b and c EStG), the appropriate number of VAK must be determined in each individual case"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The Felzmann income taxation of farmers and foresters, in Section C, Note"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "27 (p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "523) serve as a guide on the average labor requirement in special branches of business"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "Example: agricultural use according to"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "EW notification 22 ha comparative value ------------------------------------------ DM 40,000 Leased land agr"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "Use 4 ha comparison value ------------------------------------------- 7500 DM - ------------------------------------------ 26 ha ------ - DM 47,500 special crop ------------------------------- 2 ha comparison value ------------ ------------------------------ 10,000 DMIs The company employs: owner, wife (4 people in the household), son over 18 Years (without an employment contract), a permanent external worker"}, {"meta": {"name": "0023358.xml"}, "text": "The special culture a